strings.Value: "Nyrissa seemed very eager for you to serve her..."
{n}Valerie looks coldly at her monstrous counterpart, lying defeated.{/n} "This is what 'perfection' is worth."
"Her desires were vain and her judgment was wrong. I might not always agree with your decisions, {name}. But having once selected a leader, I will never betray or backstab {mf|him|her}."
"Her desires were vain and her judgment was wrong. Know that I consider it an honor to serve you, and I won't back down, even in the face of death."
"Her lies could never reach my heart. You must know this better than anyone." {n}Valerie smiles faintly.{/n}
